txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Sticky filth from insects and spiders surrounding Oatbarton. You can make the delivery to Ponto Oats at Oatbarton centre.
'We'll need to find a way to separate the good from bad in this, but it might make good fertilizer. Thank you.'
'The filth from the insects and spiders in the area might make fertilizer for our fields, if properly used and separated.'
The townsfolk in Oatbarton await the delivery of sticky filth to Ponto Oats at the centre of the town.
Deliver the sticky filth to Ponto Oats in the centre of Oatbarton
You have been tasked with collecting and delivering sticky filth from insects and spiders surrounding Oatbarton. You are to deliver the items to Ponto Oats at the centre of the town of Oatbarton.
Wanted: Sticky filth from insects and spiders surrounding Oatbarton.
